Package org.universAAL.maven.treebuilder

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DependencyTreeBuilder
    Class builds one big dependency tree for given list of artifacts.
    DependencyTreeResolutionListener
    An artifact resolution listener that constructs a dependency tree.
    ExecutionListCreator
    This class provides creation of OSGi bundles execution list on basis of list of maven artifacts.
    MavenProjectDescriptor
    Descriptor of maven project related to the dependency resolving process.
    MyDependencyNode  
    RootNode
    Helper class for passing arguments and return values to/from methods.
    ScopeArtifactFilter
    Filter to only retain objects in the following scopes: COMPILE, RUNTIME, PROVIDED.
